#touchpad
gnome-tweaks  also you can change windows focus way
Keyboard&Mouse Mouse Click Emulation
choose Area, click the bottom right of the touchpad for right-click 
and the bottom middle for middle-click

then three fingers will be right-click
and two fingers will be middle-click

